Description :
  The Stanley Parable - professional remake unusual fashion, where you will or will not play for the Stanley - office worker who suddenly realized that he was completely alone in the big building. You will follow the story, and you do not follow the plot. You will have a choice, and you will have no choice. The game is over and the game is over. Riddle will follow the mystery, and the rules by which the game should work will be broken, and then broken again. This world is not made for you to understand it, but we will explain to you. But as it passes slowly, you will start understanding comes and paradoxes will make sense. The game will not fight with you, she will invite you to dance.
